Class RandomDependentVariableDataProcessor

java.lang.Object
  mlflex.AbstractDataProcessor
      mlflex.AbstractDependentVariableDataProcessor
          mlflex.RandomDependentVariableDataProcessor

public class RandomDependentVariableDataProcessor
extends AbstractDependentVariableDataProcessor

This data processor generates data randomly. It is used for negative testing (ensuring that no positive result is attained when none is expected. This class generates random values for the dependent variable.

Author:
Stephen Piccolo
